```SELECT 
    j.id, 
    jm.id AS jmid, 
    jm.job_id, 
    jm.metadata, 
    j.job_type, 
    j.state, 
    j.start_time, 
    j.cluster_id 
FROM instabase.jobs (http://instabase.jobs) AS j 
LEFT JOIN job_metadata AS jm 
    ON j.id = jm.job_id 
WHERE 
    j.job_type = 'INDEXER_MOUNT' 
    AND jm.job_id IS NULL;```
